{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.018.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">L\u2019alliance de Josaphat avec Achab bl\u00e2m\u00e9e par le proph\u00e8te J\u00e9hu<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-3: cf. 2 Co 6:14-18. Ps 141:5. Ap 2:3-6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Josaphat, roi de Juda, revint en paix dans sa maison \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2","name":"2 Chroniques 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.18.34","name":"2 Chroniques 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.18.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>J\u00e9hu, fils de Hanani, le proph\u00e8te, alla au-devant de lui. Et il dit au roi Josaphat: Doit-on secourir le m\u00e9chant, et aimes-tu ceux qui ha\u00efssent l\u2019\u00c9ternel? A cause de cela, l\u2019\u00c9ternel est irrit\u00e9 contre toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3","name":"2 Chroniques 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.1","name":"2 Chroniques 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mais il s\u2019est trouv\u00e9 de bonnes choses en toi, car tu as fait dispara\u00eetre du pays les idoles, et tu as appliqu\u00e9 ton c\u0153ur \u00e0 chercher Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4","name":"2 Chroniques 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2","name":"2 Chroniques 19:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.005,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9formes dans l\u2019administration de la justice<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 4-11: cf. De 16:18-20; 1:16, 17; 17:8-11. Ps 82. Col 4:17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Josaphat resta \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Puis il fit encore une tourn\u00e9e parmi le peuple, depuis Beer-Sch\u00e9ba jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, et il les ramena \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5","name":"2 Chroniques 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3","name":"2 Chroniques 19:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il \u00e9tablit des juges dans toutes les villes fortes du pays de Juda, dans chaque ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6","name":"2 Chroniques 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4","name":"2 Chroniques 19:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et il dit aux juges: Prenez garde \u00e0 ce que vous ferez, car ce n\u2019est pas pour les hommes que vous prononcerez des jugements; c\u2019est pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui sera pr\u00e8s de vous quand vous les prononcerez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7","name":"2 Chroniques 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5","name":"2 Chroniques 19:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Maintenant, que la crainte de l\u2019\u00c9ternel soit sur vous; veillez sur vos actes, car il n\u2019y a chez l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, ni iniquit\u00e9, ni \u00e9gards pour l\u2019apparence des personnes, ni acceptation de pr\u00e9sents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8","name":"2 Chroniques 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6","name":"2 Chroniques 19:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Quand on fut de retour \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, Josaphat y \u00e9tablit aussi, pour les jugements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et pour les contestations, des L\u00e9vites, des sacrificateurs et des chefs de maisons paternelles d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9","name":"2 Chroniques 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7","name":"2 Chroniques 19:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et voici les ordres qu\u2019il leur donna: Vous agirez de la mani\u00e8re suivante dans la crainte de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, avec fid\u00e9lit\u00e9 et avec int\u00e9grit\u00e9 de c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10","name":"2 Chroniques 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8","name":"2 Chroniques 19:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.019.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Dans toute contestation qui vous sera soumise par vos fr\u00e8res, \u00e9tablis dans leurs villes, relativement \u00e0 un meurtre, \u00e0 une loi, \u00e0 un commandement, \u00e0 des pr\u00e9ceptes et \u00e0 des ordonnances, vous les \u00e9clairerez, afin qu\u2019ils ne se rendent pas coupables envers l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et que sa col\u00e8re n\u2019\u00e9clate pas sur vous et sur vos fr\u00e8res. C\u2019est ainsi que vous agirez, et vous ne serez point coupables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.11","name":"2 Chroniques 19:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9","name":"2 Chroniques 19:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 19:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.019.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.020.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.19.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et voici, vous avez \u00e0 votre t\u00eate Amaria, le souverain sacrificateur, pour toutes les affaires de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et Zebadia, fils d\u2019Isma\u00ebl, chef de la maison de Juda, pour toutes les affaires du roi, et vous avez devant vous des L\u00e9vites comme magistrats. Fortifiez-vous et agissez, et que l\u2019\u00c9ternel soit avec celui qui fera le bien!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19","name":"2 Chroniques 19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.20.1","name":"2 Chroniques 20:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.20.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10","name":"2 Chroniques 19:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.19.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc09ef034.92404026');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc09ef034.92404026\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc09ef034.92404026","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc09ef034.92404026'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc09ef034.92404026\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}